<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 10:08:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>观看：男子在布鲁克林偷走拖车，损坏多辆汽车</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/watch-man-steals-tow-truck-damages-multiple-cars-in-brooklyn/articleshow/113164087.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113164087.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;布鲁克林日落公园的​​一名愤怒男子在看到自己的车辆被拖走后偷走了一辆拖车。在与拖车司机发生肢体冲突后，他鲁莽驾驶，损坏了几辆汽车，并撞上了一辆城市公交车。该男子抛弃了卡车，步行逃离。当局正在积极寻找他。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 09:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/watch-man-steals-tow-truck-damages-multiple-cars-in-brooklyn/articleshow/113164087.cms</guid></item><item><title>母亲睡着后，两岁和四岁的两姐妹在长岛池塘溺水身亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/two-sisters-aged-2-and-4-drown-in-long-island-pond-after-mother-falls-asleep/articleshow/113164559.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113164559.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;两名年龄分别为 2 岁和 4 岁的妹妹在纽约州长岛公寓楼后面的池塘里溺水身亡。该事件发生在周六下午3点15分左右。他们在被报告失踪并在石溪大学医院被宣布死亡后不久被发现。目前当局正在调查此案。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 09:27:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/two-sisters-aged-2-and-4-drown-in-long-island-pond-after-mother-falls-asleep/articleshow/113164559.cms</guid></item><item><title>“不是事实”：蒂姆·沃尔兹批评 JD·万斯关于校园枪击事件的言论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/not-a-fact-tim-walz-criticises-jd-vances-remark-on-school-shootings/articleshow/113161692.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113161692.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;州长蒂姆·沃尔兹 (Tim Walz) 批评 JD·万斯 (JD Vance) 关于校园枪击事件不可避免的言论。他在人权运动全国晚宴上发表讲话，强调了学校安全和 LGBTQ+ 权利的重要性。沃尔兹与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯概述了他的议程，重点是减少工薪家庭的税收和通过《平等法案》来禁止歧视。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 08:57:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/not-a-fact-tim-walz-criticises-jd-vances-remark-on-school-shootings/articleshow/113161692.cms</guid></item><item><title>西班牙向委内瑞拉反对派领导人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯·乌鲁蒂亚提供庇护</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/spain-to-grant-asylum-to-venezuelan-opposition-leader-edmundo-gonzalez-urrutia/articleshow/113165430.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113165430.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;西班牙外交部长证实将为委内瑞拉反对派领导人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯·乌鲁蒂亚提供庇护。在挑战马杜罗总统的连任并面临逮捕令后，冈萨雷斯在西班牙驻加拉加斯大使馆寻求庇护。他乘坐西班牙军用飞机离开委内瑞拉，马杜罗政府为了政治和平而允许安全通行。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 08:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/spain-to-grant-asylum-to-venezuelan-opposition-leader-edmundo-gonzalez-urrutia/articleshow/113165430.cms</guid></item><item><title>“杰出的年轻人”：佛罗里达州高中橄榄球运动员钱斯·盖纳在比赛中倒地后死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/exceptional-young-man-florida-high-school-football-player-chance-gainer-dies-after-collapsing-during-game/articleshow/113163454.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113163454.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;来自佛罗里达州的 18 岁高中橄榄球运动员 Chance Gainer 在佐治亚州的一场比赛中不幸倒地身亡。他最近访问了范德比尔特大学，希望在那里踢足球。盖纳在突然去世前两次达阵。随着当局的调查，他倒地的原因仍不清楚。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 07:26:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/exceptional-young-man-florida-high-school-football-player-chance-gainer-dies-after-collapsing-during-game/articleshow/113163454.cms</guid></item><item><title>“哈里在英国仍有主力”：王子与家人的“秘密”联系</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/harry-still-has-an-anchor-in-the-uk-princes-secret-connection-with-family-members/articleshow/113163307.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113163307.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;尽管与威廉王子和查尔斯国王疏远，哈里王子仍然与已故母亲戴安娜王妃的家人保持联系。他参加了简·费罗斯夫人丈夫的葬礼，并与叔叔查尔斯·斯宾塞一起住在奥尔索普别墅。此外，他与表弟比阿特丽斯公主保持着良好的关系，她在他和威廉之间进行调解。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 06:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/harry-still-has-an-anchor-in-the-uk-princes-secret-connection-with-family-members/articleshow/113163307.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国总统拜登离任532天，4年请假48年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-spent-532-days-away-from-office-took-48-years-worth-of-leave-in-4-years/articleshow/113162558.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113162558.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登在不到四年的时间里休假了532天，远远超过了他的前任。批评者认为，他的频繁缺席忽视了通货膨胀和边境安全等关键问题。虽然助手们声称他在假期期间远程工作，但他放松的公开形象引发了关于平衡总统职责与个人休假的争论。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 06:23:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-president-biden-spent-532-days-away-from-office-took-48-years-worth-of-leave-in-4-years/articleshow/113162558.cms</guid></item><item><title>委内瑞拉反对派前总统候选人为何逃离该国：关键细节</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-venezuelan-opposition-ex-presidential-candidate-fled-the-country-key-details/articleshow/113162204.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113162204.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;委内瑞拉反对派领导人埃德蒙多·冈萨雷斯在有争议的总统选举结果有利于尼古拉斯·马杜罗后因逮捕令躲藏起来，在西班牙寻求庇护。委内瑞拉允许他安全离开该国，强调遵守国际法，并致力于在与巴西持续紧张的外交紧张局势中实现政治和平。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 05:15:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/why-venezuelan-opposition-ex-presidential-candidate-fled-the-country-key-details/articleshow/113162204.cms</guid></item><item><title>乔治亚州枪击案嫌疑人的母亲在枪击前几分钟给学校打电话，警告“极端紧急情况”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-shooter-suspects-mother-called-school-minutes-before-shooting-warned-of-extreme-emergency/articleshow/113161025.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113161025.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在乔治亚州校园枪击事件发生之前，玛西·格雷向学校辅导员通报了她儿子柯尔特的情况。玛西通过柯尔特发来的短信联系了学校。阿巴拉奇高中发生枪击事件，造成四人死亡、九人受伤。柯尔特和他的父亲都面临严重的法律指控。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 05:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-shooter-suspects-mother-called-school-minutes-before-shooting-warned-of-extreme-emergency/articleshow/113161025.cms</guid></item><item><title>因公众愤怒，澳大利亚 2026 年人口普查将纳入 LGBTIQ+ 身份问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australias-2026-census-to-include-lgbtiq-identity-questions-following-public-outrage/articleshow/113161949.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113161949.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚 2026 年人口普查将首次包括针对 16 岁及以上个人的性取向和性别的可选问题。这一决定是在他们最初被排除在外引起争议之后作出的。政府官员强调，这一变化旨在确保 LGBTIQ+ 群体的代表性，反映他们在国家统计数据中的重要性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 05:05:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australias-2026-census-to-include-lgbtiq-identity-questions-following-public-outrage/articleshow/113161949.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国男子工作104天休息1天身亡 公司追究责任</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-man-dies-after-working-for-104-days-with-1-day-off-company-held-liable/articleshow/113161351.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113161351.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 30岁的画家阿宝，在连续104天只休息一天的艰苦工作后，因多脏器衰竭去世。法院判决该公司承担20%的责任，并责令其家属赔偿。他的工作条件违反了中国劳动法关于工作时间的规定。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 04:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/chinese-man-dies-after-working-for-104-days-with-1-day-off-company-held-liable/articleshow/113161351.cms</guid></item><item><title>“我们是由愚蠢的人统治的”：特朗普呼吁修改宪法以罢免“密谋”副总统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/were-run-by-stupid-people-trump-calls-for-constitutional-change-to-remove-conspiring-vice-presidents/articleshow/113160223.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160223.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普提议修改第25条修正案，罢免掩盖总统无能的副总统。这一呼吁是在威斯康星州的一次竞选集会上做出的，是为了回应乔·拜登糟糕的辩论表现以及随后退出总统竞选，卡马拉·哈里斯因此成为民主党提名人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:37:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/were-run-by-stupid-people-trump-calls-for-constitutional-change-to-remove-conspiring-vice-presidents/articleshow/113160223.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国圣贝纳迪诺气温突破三位数，肆虐的野火迫使人们疏散</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/raging-wildfire-forces-evacuations-in-us-san-bernardino-as-temperatures-cross-triple-digits/articleshow/113160573.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160573.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;洛杉矶附近的圣贝纳迪诺国家森林发生野火，气温高达 112°F，导致人员疏散。星期四晚上发生的线火已经烧毁了 11 平方英里的植被。超过 500 名消防员在空中支援下赶赴现场。官员警告说，未来 12 小时内火势可能会严重蔓延。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/raging-wildfire-forces-evacuations-in-us-san-bernardino-as-temperatures-cross-triple-digits/articleshow/113160573.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国认为伊朗已向俄罗斯转让短程弹道导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia/articleshow/113160521.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160521.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国认为伊朗已向俄罗斯转让短程弹道导弹用于乌克兰战争，引发了对冲突升级和欧洲安全威胁的担忧。白宫重申对此类转让的警告，而伊朗则否认提供武器，并呼吁停火。中央情报局局长强调了涉及俄罗斯、中国、伊朗和朝鲜的令人不安的防务关系。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-believes-iran-has-transferred-short-range-ballistic-missiles-to-russia/articleshow/113160521.cms</guid></item><item><title>卡玛拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普将在首场辩论中对峙：规则是什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-and-donald-trump-to-face-off-in-first-debate-what-are-the-rules/articleshow/113160440.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160440.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡马拉·哈里斯和唐纳德·特朗普将于 9 月 10 日进行首次直接辩论。这场辩论由 ABC 新闻在费城国家宪法中心主办，时长 90 分钟，包括定时回答和静音麦克风，以确保辩论顺利进行。辩论将在全国范围内转播，没有现场观众。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-presidential-elections-kamala-harris-and-donald-trump-to-face-off-in-first-debate-what-are-the-rules/articleshow/113160440.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 透露了 SpaceX 将无人驾驶星际飞船送往火星的雄心勃勃的计划：我们所知道的</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-reveals-spacexs-ambitious-plan-to-send-uncrewed-starships-to-mars-what-we-know/articleshow/113160287.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160287.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;埃隆·马斯克宣布，SpaceX 将在两年内向火星发射第一艘无人驾驶星际飞船，旨在测试其着陆可靠性。如果成功，载人任务将在四年内进行。最终目标是在大约 20 年内在火星上建立一座自给自足的城市。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:14:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-reveals-spacexs-ambitious-plan-to-send-uncrewed-starships-to-mars-what-we-know/articleshow/113160287.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗特勤局特工因在欧洲范围内密谋杀害犹太人而在法国被拘留</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iranian-secret-service-agents-detained-in-france-for-europe-wide-plot-to-kill-jews/articleshow/113160024.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113160024.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; Abdelkrim S 和 Sabrina B 因涉嫌参与伊朗支持的针对德国和法国犹太人的暗杀阴谋而受到巴黎一家法院的指控。这对夫妇被指控与恐怖组织合谋，目前被审前拘留。调查还将其与对以色列企业的纵火企图联系起来。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 02:01:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/iranian-secret-service-agents-detained-in-france-for-europe-wide-plot-to-kill-jews/articleshow/113160024.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国肯塔基州高速公路多人遭枪击，追捕“武装”嫌疑人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/multiple-people-shot-along-highway-in-us-state-of-kentucky-hunt-for-armed-suspect-on/articleshow/113159936.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113159936.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在肯塔基州南部，75 号州际公路的一段路段因枪击事件而关闭，造成多人受伤。当局正在寻找嫌疑人约瑟夫·库奇，他被认为携带武器且危险。劳雷尔县治安官办公室和肯塔基州警方建议居民在追捕嫌疑人期间留在室内。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 01:21:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/multiple-people-shot-along-highway-in-us-state-of-kentucky-hunt-for-armed-suspect-on/articleshow/113159936.cms</guid></item><item><title>佐治亚州校园枪击案嫌疑人柯尔特·格雷在案发前曾住在几处出租房中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-colt-gray-lived-in-several-rental-homes-prior-to-the-incident/articleshow/113159693.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113159693.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 14 岁犯罪嫌疑人柯尔特·格雷 (Colt Gray) 和他的父亲科林 (Colin) 因在佐治亚州阿巴拉奇高中杀害两名学生和两名教师而面临指控。科林离婚后，一家人多次搬家。柯尔特饱受欺凌和父母分居的困扰。他因这起事件而作为成年人接受审判。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 00:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/georgia-school-shooting-suspect-colt-gray-lived-in-several-rental-homes-prior-to-the-incident/articleshow/113159693.cms</guid></item><item><title>哈里王子将在 40 岁后获得主要遗产。他将得到......</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-set-to-receive-major-inheritance-after-he-turns-40-he-will-get-/articleshow/113157399.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/113157399.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈里王子将于 9 月 15 日庆祝他的 40 岁生日，他将从一个家庭信托基金中收到约 800 万英镑。该基金由他的曾祖母于 1994 年设立，旨在为她的曾孙提供经济礼物。通过与 Spotify、Netflix 的交易和图书合同，这对夫妇的财富不断增加，财务上的增长也随之增加。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:21:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/prince-harry-set-to-receive-major-inheritance-after-he-turns-40-he-will-get-/articleshow/113157399.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>